            "endSection": "sections.0"
        }, 
        {
            "offsetInBeginSection": 664, 
            "offsetInEndSection": 850, 
            "text": "Most cases were sporadic, but in addition there were instances of both autosomal dominant and autosomal recessive inheritance, while two families showed mosaicism for dominant mutations.", 
